{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cee38c3a-0ae1-4de7-b51b-e73a1c49eae9","content":"Let me also check the broader template structure to give a complete assessment.","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_wUiLfQNbyeFlOwYfFIxtbv","name":"view","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-410995578bbb44ba9edfffd38dd80320"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"view the file at /tmp/sv-410995578bbb44ba9edfffd38dd80320."}],"interactionId":"51f889b3-9123-43c6-9f8b-08a087d34770","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me review this template.json for NuGet publishing readiness. I'll check against the .NET template engine schema requirements.\n\nKey issues I see:\n\n1. **Missing `$schema`** — Not strictly required, but strongly recommended for validation and editor support.\n2. **Missing `groupIdentity`** — Recommended for NuGet publishing so templates can be grouped.\n3. **Missing `precedence`** — Useful when multiple versions of a template exist.\n4. **Missing `preferNameDirectory`** — Minor, but useful.\n5. **The `Framework` symbol** — The symbol is defined but there's no `replaces` to actually substitute the value in project files. \n\nThis is the real problem — when users select a framework, it won't actually get written into the generated project files. The other missing properties like `defaultName` and `sourceName` validation are less critical, though the `sourceName` value of \"MyWebApi\" should match what's in your template source files. The `classifications` and `tags` look appropriate.\n\nThe core issue is that the `Framework` symbol needs either a `replaces` property to substitute the value into files like the .csproj's `<TargetFramework>` element, or the template source files need to reference it through conditionals. Without one of those mechanisms, the framework choice becomes inert. I should check if there are other template files in the directory that might reveal how this symbol is actually being used.","outputTokens":532,"requestId":"403F:204131:EE6BF7B:107A2509:69EC0F92"},"id":"92f08fb4-7f67-4140-9e9f-c6e438864858","timestamp":"2026-04-25T00:49:36.637Z","parentId":"67472701-78af-4ace-b406-b9945f1655ef"}
